<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Open Questions — {{FEATURE_NAME}}</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="spec.css">
</head>
<body>
<div class="page-wrap">

  <nav class="sidebar" aria-label="Table of contents">
    <p class="sidebar-title">Contents</p>
    <div id="toc-list"></div>
  </nav>

  <div class="main-content">
    <header class="spec-header">
      <h1>Open Questions — {{FEATURE_NAME}}</h1>

      <table class="meta-table">
        <tbody>
          <tr><th>Feature</th>         <td><code>{{FEATURE_NAME}}</code></td></tr>
          <tr><th>Feature slug</th>    <td><code>{{FEATURE_SLUG}}</code></td></tr>
          <tr><th>Source document</th> <td><code>{{SOURCE_DOCUMENT}}</code></td></tr>
          <tr><th>Task ID</th>         <td><code>{{TASK_ID}}</code></td></tr>
          <tr><th>Created</th>         <td><code>{{CREATED_DATE}}</code></td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </header>

    <main>

      <section id="purpose">
        <h2>Purpose</h2>
        <p>This document records unresolved questions found while converting the source material into an SDD spec.</p>
        <p>Blocking questions must be answered before implementation.</p>
      </section>

      <hr>

      <section id="question-status-summary">
        <h2>Question status summary</h2>

        <table>
          <thead>
            <tr><th>Type</th><th style="text-align:right">Count</th></tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr><td><span class="badge badge-blocking">Blocking</span></td>     <td style="text-align:right">{{BLOCKING_COUNT}}</td></tr>
            <tr><td><span class="badge badge-warning">Non-blocking</span></td>  <td style="text-align:right">{{NON_BLOCKING_COUNT}}</td></tr>
            <tr><td><span class="badge badge-ok">Resolved</span></td>           <td style="text-align:right">{{RESOLVED_COUNT}}</td></tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>

        <p><strong>Blocking questions present:</strong></p>
        <pre><code>{{BLOCKING_QUESTIONS_PRESENT}}</code></pre>
      </section>

      <hr>

      <section id="open-questions">
        <h2>Open questions</h2>

        <!-- Repeat this card block for each open question.
             Add class="blocking-yes" to .card for blocking questions. -->
        <div class="card blocking-yes" id="q1">
          <div class="card-header">
            <span class="req-id err">Q1</span>
            <span class="card-title">{{QUESTION_TITLE}}</span>
            <span class="badge badge-blocking">Blocking</span>
          </div>
          <div class="card-body">
            <dl class="card-fields">
              <dt>Question</dt>                        <dd>{{QUESTION_TEXT}}</dd>
              <dt>Why it matters</dt>                  <dd>{{WHY_IT_MATTERS}}</dd>
              <dt>Blocking</dt>                        <dd>{{BLOCKING}}</dd>
              <dt>Default assumption if not answered</dt><dd>{{DEFAULT_ASSUMPTION}}</dd>
              <dt>Affected files / sections</dt>       <dd>{{AFFECTED_FILE_OR_SECTION}}</dd>
              <dt>Related requirements</dt>            <dd>{{RELATED_REQUIREMENT}}</dd>
              <dt>Decision</dt>                        <dd><span class="badge badge-pending">Pending</span></dd>
              <dt>Resolved by</dt>                     <dd>Pending</dd>
              <dt>Resolved at</dt>                     <dd>Pending</dd>
            </dl>
          </div>
        </div>

      </section>

      <hr>

      <section id="resolved-questions">
        <h2>Resolved questions</h2>
        <p>Move questions here after the developer answers them.</p>
        <!-- Example resolved question:
        <div class="card" id="q1-resolved">
          <div class="card-header">
            <span class="req-id">Q1</span>
            <span class="card-title">Default result limit</span>
            <span class="badge badge-ok">Resolved</span>
          </div>
          <div class="card-body">
            <dl class="card-fields">
              <dt>Question</dt>     <dd>How many notes should <code>notes recent</code> show by default?</dd>
              <dt>Decision</dt>     <dd>Show 5 notes by default.</dd>
              <dt>Resolved by</dt>  <dd>developer</dd>
              <dt>Resolved at</dt>  <dd>YYYY-MM-DD</dd>
            </dl>
          </div>
        </div>
        -->
      </section>

      <hr>

      <section id="deferred-questions">
        <h2>Deferred questions</h2>
        <p>Move non-blocking questions here if the developer explicitly decides to defer them. Deferred questions must not block implementation.</p>
        <!-- Example deferred question:
        <div class="card" id="q3-deferred">
          <div class="card-header">
            <span class="req-id">Q3</span>
            <span class="card-title">Exact empty-state copy</span>
            <span class="badge badge-warning">Deferred</span>
          </div>
          <div class="card-body">
            <dl class="card-fields">
              <dt>Question</dt>           <dd>What exact empty-state text should be used?</dd>
              <dt>Deferred decision</dt>  <dd>Use the default copy for now and revisit after UX review.</dd>
              <dt>Temporary behavior</dt> <dd>Use "No notes found."</dd>
              <dt>Resolved by</dt>        <dd>developer</dd>
              <dt>Resolved at</dt>        <dd>YYYY-MM-DD</dd>
            </dl>
          </div>
        </div>
        -->
      </section>

      <hr>

      <section id="notes-for-claude-code">
        <h2>Notes for Claude Code</h2>
        <div class="claude-note">
          <h4>Rules Claude Code must follow</h4>
          <ol>
            <li>If any question has <strong>Blocking: Yes</strong> and <strong>Decision: Pending</strong>, do not implement.</li>
            <li>If only non-blocking questions remain, the task may be marked <code>spec_ready</code> if all assumptions are explicit.</li>
            <li>Do not answer product, security, data, billing, or architecture questions silently.</li>
            <li>When the developer answers a question, update this file and reflect the decision in <code>requirements.html</code>, <code>design.html</code>, <code>tasks.html</code>, or <code>acceptance-tests.html</code>.</li>
            <li>Before moving a task to <code>human_approved</code>, verify that no blocking question remains pending.</li>
          </ol>
        </div>
      </section>

    </main>
  </div><!-- /.main-content -->
</div><!-- /.page-wrap -->
<script src="spec.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
